@node "Register" "How to Register"
@{b}HOW TO REGISTER@{ub}

The "Windows" and "Screen" pages are disabled if the program is not
registered.  All other features are fully functional.

It costs only 5 US dollars to register MUIWBPattern!  Just send the cash
or check along with the form below.

I will send you a serial number and instructions on how to enable all the
features on the program through email (if you include your email address),
or on paper through the postal service.

Once you register, you will be able to use the "Windows" and "Screen"
pages.  Your serial number will work with any future shareware releases of
MUIWBPattern.


